  %h1.title Methodic.io
%main
  %h2.subheading.first Methodic the Software Consultancy
  %p
    Methodic provides Ruby and Javascript, full-stack web development and software consulting as a service. We offer our services in London, Reading and Oxford, but are just as capable of working remotely from our office in South Oxfordshire.
  %p
    Apologies for the lack of details, but this website is merely a placeholder while a more informative and feature rich site is in development. If you wish to find out more about how Methodic can help you with your software, please feel free to contact the founder,
    = succeed "." do
      %a{:href => "mailto:ed@methodic.io"} Edward Minnett
  %p
    To get a sense of what Methodic can offer, please feel free to browse Edward's experience as illustrated by his
    = succeed "." do
      %a{:href => "https://www.linkedin.com/in/eminnett"} LinkedIn profile
  %h2.subheading Methodic the Research Endeavour
  %p
    Methodic also invests time exploring the application of data science and machine learning in the pursuit of knowledge discovery. It is clear that these disciplines are becoming increasingly important in the world of web application development and our hope is that this investment will help Methodic to provide an excelent service for our clients. Our hope is that this website will eventually act as a platform to share much of this research.
